26
00:04:29,602 --> 00:04:31,303
<i>And Jumping Jack Flash,</i>
<i>the four year old</i>

27
00:04:31,304 --> 00:04:33,405
<i>from Stanton Stables</i>
<i>moves directly in the front.</i>

28
00:04:33,406 --> 00:04:37,609
<i>Followed by</i>
<i>Oh, My Darling.</i>

29
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:39,278
