about you.

244
00:14:44,117 --> 00:14:45,484
<i>I can have that look</i>
<i>without seeing Etta.</i>

245
00:14:47,420 --> 00:14:48,821
Looks like
she's running the place

246
00:14:48,822 --> 00:14:50,089
on her own.

247
00:14:50,090 --> 00:14:51,957
<i>That bunch down</i>
<i>at the mercantile's going on</i>

248
00:14:51,958 --> 00:14:54,960
about how homer's got
"the olds-heimer's disease,"

249
00:14:54,961 --> 00:14:56,261
though I doubt
he's any worse off

250
00:14:56,262 --> 00:14:58,297
than those dimwits telling it.

251
00:14:58,298 --> 00:15:01,066
